java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class Panel
extends javax.swing.JPanel

A Panel has 5 JLabels, a JTextField, and 2 JComboBoxes. It calls Display and sends user input to Display and Processor.
